Opinions: Hi Koja! For opinions as a player I think you actually know how to play the game and are a great player on Apollo. You've improved so much since the old Necromancy a long time ago. However, I feel like you still have quite a lot of space for improvement, so make sure to work hard (if you want to continue minecraft).

I actually really like onions...green onions, red onions, white onions...well it depends what the onions are in but I don’t mind them
